11#include "ipf.h"
12
13mb_t *dupmbt(orig)
14 mb_t *orig;
15{
16 mb_t *m;
17
18 m = (mb_t *)malloc(sizeof(mb_t));
19 if (m == NULL)
20 return NULL;
21 m->mb_len = orig->mb_len;
22 m->mb_next = NULL;
23 m->mb_data = (char *)m->mb_buf + (orig->mb_data - (char *)orig->mb_buf);
24 bcopy(orig->mb_data, m->mb_data, m->mb_len);
25 return m;
26}
